		"Text": "亲爱的@，^今天是第一届Joja员工感谢日！^我想要邀请你作为我们的特邀来宾。如果你有空的话，请务必光临！^- 克里斯托夫^又及：随信附上前往祖祖城的500g车费。注意安全。%item money 500 %%[textcolor black]", // Text of the letter. You can use @ to put the players name and ^ for line breaks. You can also use the base game commands to add money, items and stuff. If an translation file is provide, you should put a translation key here.
		"LetterBG": "assets/jojaLetterBG.png",
		"Repeatable": false, // If true the mod won't check it the letter Id has already been delivered. Default is false.
